{"data":[{"id":564407208,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/564407208","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546360912,"updated_time":1546362188,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"nobody","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e我们老师说：像数学系的学生，上到研究生阶段，才刚准备接触100年以内的数学\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然这种现象在物理系也存在，但是，可能仅仅是属于数学系和物理系的特有现象\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e偏巧，哥德巴赫猜想过去100年以内还没人证出来过，陈景润那已经是最接近答案的未完成的证明，别说100年以内，估摸着也就是50年以内的数学，估计你得到博士研究生阶段才接上轨\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果证出来了呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e别说，这种情况完全可能发生！\u003c/b\u003e如果你指的是那个很多年才出一个的才华横溢的伽罗瓦的话，他16岁才开始系统学习数学，结果没几年居然（初步）搞出了个至今仍困扰我们这些学生的群论。如果你让伽罗瓦和正常学生一样，从7岁开始上小学一年级\u003cb\u003e（但注意是最好的教育，而不是填鸭式教育）\u003c/b\u003e，然后以比常人快的速度给他灌输数学知识，那么，估计刚上初中那会基本就把数学系本科阶段的学习任务给弄完了，可能在高中阶段真的就能解决哥德巴赫猜想（\u003cb\u003e只是存在可能性而已\u003c/b\u003e）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003ci\u003e但问题来了，你究竟想讨论啥？\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e答案不是很明确吗？如果证出来了，他才华横溢，一定会被保送，出国深造也完全是在情理之中\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e证不出来，但是能跟那些试图证明这个定理的前辈做到同一水平的，比如能（独立）写出跟陈景润那样水平的证明，那也是才华横溢，照样能被保送\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e证明过程狗屁不通，甚至根本写不出来的，不用想了，还是普通人而已\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"我们老师说：像数学系的学生，上到研究生阶段，才刚准备接触100年以内的数学当然这种现象在物理系也存在，但是，可能仅仅是属于数学系和物理系的特有现象偏巧，哥德巴赫猜想过去100年以内还没人证出来过，陈景润那已经是最接近答案的未完成的证明，别说100…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=1354\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment